K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-17: sgo sna tshogs nas bstan cing sgo mtha' yas pa'i
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-18: dbyibs rnam pa sna tshogs su 'dug pa'i rnam par
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-19: phye ba sna tshogs dang ldan pa'i 'jig rten gyi
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-20: khams rgya mtsho thams cad du byang chub sems dpa'i
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-22: byang chub sems dpa'i skyon med pa yongs su mnan nas byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-23: rnam par 'phrul pas rgyas par dgang bar bya ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-24: thugs kyi skad cig re re la dus gsum gyi
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-25: sangs rgyas kyi 'phrin las ma lus pa thams cad
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-26: sems can pha rol gyi sems dang bsam pas rnam
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-27: par dmigs par bya ba'i phyir 'gro ba thams cad
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47a-28: la thams cad mkhyen pa'i bsod nams rgya mtsho'i shugs
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-0: mngon par sgrub @47b pa mdzad par gyur pas mngon par shes so //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-3: de ltar bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa rnam
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-4: par snang mdzad sngon byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-5: mdzad pa'i tshe 'jig rten gnas pa bsod nams dang
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-6: ye shes kyi tshogs dang bral ba /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-7: sems can byas pa drin du mi gzo bas yongs su gang ba /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-8: mi shes pa'i mun pas chod pa; bdag tu bya ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-9: bdag gir bya ba la mngon par zhen pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-10: ma rig pa'i mun pa rab rib kyis bsgribs pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-11: tshul bzhin ma yin par rnam par rtog pa la
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-12: zhugs pa; lta ba thibs po bas dgon par mgo
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-13: brlags pa / rgyu dang 'bras bu la mgo rmongs pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-14: nyon mongs pa dang las kyi dbang du gyur pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-15: 'khor ba'i mya ngam chen po'i sdug bsngal gyi sa'i 'og tu lhung ba /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-16: phongs pa'i sdug bsngal sna tshogs nyams su myong bar
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-17: gyur pa rnams la thugs rje chen po bskyed de
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-18: / pha rol tu phyin pa sbyang ba'i sprin chen
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-19: po mngon par bsgrubs te dge ba'i rtsa ba la
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-21: yongs su bsngags pa dang sems can thams cad kyi
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-22: 'khor ba'i phongs pa'i sdug bsngal rnam par bzlog pa
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-23: dang / bsod nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen po la mngon par mos par bya ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:47b-24: rgyu'i dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs mngon par bstan pa dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-1: ba'i phyogs rab tu brjod pa dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-2: sangs rgyas kyi chos kyi dkyil 'khor yongs su bsdu ba'i phyogs snang bar bya ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-3: sems can thams cad kyi mos pa'i phyogs rab tu brjod par bya ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-4: sems can thams cad kyi zhing yongs su sgrub pa'i phyogs legs par bstan pa dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-5: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi rigs mi gcad
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-6: pa'i phyogs kyi rjes su 'brang bar bya ba dang
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-7: / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi bstan pa'i phyogs yongs su gzung ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-8: mi dge ba'i chos thams cad kyi phyogs rnam par bzlog pa dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-9: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi tshogs kyi phyogs yongs su brjod pa mdzad de /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-10: pha rol tu phyin pa'i sprin chen pos sems can
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-11: gyi khams thams cad rgyas par bkang ste mngon par
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-12: bsgrubs nas bsam pa ji lta ba bzhin du sems
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-13: can tshim par 'gyur bar chos kyis shin tu bsdu
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-14: ba la sems can rab tu dgod par mdzad do
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-15: // thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi tshogs la yang dag par bskul to //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-16: byang chub sems dpa'i pha rol tu phyin pa chen po la rab tu btsud do //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-17: 'phags pa'i nor thams cad rab tu thob par bya bas nye bar bstan to //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-18: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid du 'dun pa'i shugs kyis
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48a-19: sems can rnams dge ba'i rtsa ba rgya mtsho rnam
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-1: de bzhin gshegs pa rnam par 'phrul pa'i sgor yang de dag rab tu btsud de /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-2: phung po shin tu zhi ba'i bde bas yongs su bsdu ba bsdus te /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-3: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bdag nyid che ba la mngon
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-4: du mos par byas nas byang chub sems dpas yongs
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-5: su bzung ba'i ye shes la rab tu bkod do
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-7: 'phags ma khyod bla na med pa yang dag par
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-8: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu yang dag par zhugs nas
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-13: yid ches par dka' ba ste /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-18: khong du chud par dka' ba ste /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-19: lha dang bcas pa'i 'jig rten dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-20: nyan thos dang rang sangs rgyas thams cad kyis kyang khong du chud par mi nus so //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-21: gzhan du na de bzhin gshegs pa'i byin gyi rlabs dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-22: dge ba'i bshes gnyen gyis yongs su bzung ba ma gtogs te /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-24: sems can 'khor ba'i bde ba thams cad la mngon par 'dod pa med pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-25: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bde ba la lhag par dmigs pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-26: sems can thams cad kyi sdug bsngal dang yid mi
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-27: bde ba rab tu zhi bar bya ba la zhugs
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-28: pa / de bzhin gshegs pa'i yon tan rgya mtsho
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:48b-29: la 'jug pa'i nan tan la mngon par mos pa
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-1: chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin nges par rtogs pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-2: nam mkha'i spyod yul dang ldan pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-3: mos pa yangs pa'i lam gyis rnam par dag pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-4: 'khor ba'i rgyun las phyir phyogs pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-5: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes rgya mtsho la mngon par mos pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-6: chos kyi grong khyer du 'gro bar gcig tu chad pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-7: de bzhin gshegs pa'i yul yongs su gnon pa'i brtson 'grus can /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-8: sangs rgyas kyi sa'i rgyud rnam par gnon pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-9: thams cad mkhyen pa'i stobs yongs su rdzogs par bya ba la mngon par mos pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-10: stobs bcu rab tu thob par bya ba'i mthar thug pa rnams kyis bsod nams dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-11: ye shes kyi tshogs yangs pas nye bar bsten pa'i sems dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-12: bsam pa rnam par dag pa dang ma zhum pa /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-13: nyon mongs pa med pa dang ma yo ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-16: mun pa med pa'i sems dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-17: ye shes kyi snang ba kun tu snang bas snang bar gyur pa'i sems dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-18: sems can thams cad la phan pa dang bde bar bya bar shin tu 'dun pa'i sems dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-19: bdud kyi 'khor dang nyon mongs pa thams cad kyis mi thub pa'i sems dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-20: thams cad mkhyen pa nyid kyi ye shes thob par
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49a-21: bya bar skabs phye ba'i sems kyis kyang khong du
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-2: yid ches par bya ba dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-5: shes par bya ba mi nus so //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-9: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyi yul te /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-10: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad kyis yongs su ma non na /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-11: sems can gzhan thams cad kyis lta ci zhig smos /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-12: 'on kyang sems can cang shes rnams kyi bsam pa
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-13: phun sum tshogs pa rnam par dag par bya ba
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-14: dang / dge ba'i rtsa ba la spyod pa'i sems
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-15: can rnams kyi lhag pa'i bsam pa dbang du 'gyur
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-17: khyod kyis bsam pa thag pa nas yongs su dris
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-18: pa'i lung bstan pa'i chos nyid rab tu 'byung ba
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-19: thob par bya ba'i phyir de bzhin gshegs pa'i byin
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-20: gyis bstan to // de nas mtshan mo'i lha mo
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-21: shing thams cad kyi me tog rgyas pas bde bar
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-22: gnas pas de'i tshe don de nyid brnan te bstan
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-23: pa'i phyir dus gsum du byung ba'i de bzhin gshegs
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-24: pa'i yul la rnam par bltas te tshigs su bcad
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-26: sangs rgyas sras po khyod kyis gang dris pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-27: de ni bsam yas zab mo sangs rgyas yul //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-28: bsam yas zhing gi rdul phran rab snyed kyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-29: bskal pa mang pos de kun brjod mi nus //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:49b-30: sems can 'dod pa'i sems ldan sdang ba dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-1: gti mug mun pas bsgribs pa dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-2: 'chab dang dregs pas bsam pa nyams gyur pas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-3: rgyal ba'i chos nyid zhi ba shes mi nus //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-4: phrag dog 'jungs pa'i dbang gi rjes 'brang dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-5: g-yo sgyus bsam pa rnyog par gyur pa dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-6: nyon mongs las kyi sgrib pas bsgribs pa yis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-7: sangs rgyas yul 'di shes par mi nus so //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-8: phung po khams dang skye mched gnas pa dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-9: 'jig tshogs mang la gnas par gyur pa dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-10: lta sems 'du shes phyin ci log gyur pas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-11: zhi ba'i sa 'di shes par mi nus so //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-12: rgyal ba'i yul ni shes dka' zhi ba ste //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-13: rang bzhin dri med rnam par rtog pa med //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-14: srid par brten cing 'khor la chags pa yis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-15: chos 'di yang dag shes par mi nus so //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-16: sangs rgyas rigs su rigs ldan gang skyes pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-17: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyis byin brlabs shing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-18: chos kyi rgyal po'i gdung rabs yongs 'dzin pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-19: drang srong de dag yul ni 'di yin no //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-20: dkar chos rgya mtshos mi ngoms sems ldan zhing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-21: gang rnams dge ba'i bshes kyis yongs bzung ste //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-22: thub pa'i stobs la dmigs pa'i sems sprin can //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-23: de dag 'di thos bzod pa thob par 'gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50a-24: gang rnams bsam pa dri med rnams rtog med //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-0: bar snang @50b mkha' bzhin phyogs dang phyogs mtshams su //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-1: mun pa rnam bsal blo gros sgron ma'i sprin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-2: dri med de dag spyod yul 'di yin no //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-3: snying rje'i bsam pas 'gro ba rgya mtsho rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-4: dus gsum byung ba gang rnams rgyas byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-5: sems can ma lus rjes 'brang byams pa can //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-6: de dag rgyal ba'i tshul 'dir 'jug par 'gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-7: gang rnams 'dzin med dga' ba'i sems ldan zhing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-8: rtag par bdog pa thams cad sbyin brtson la //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-9: sems can kun la mnyam par zhugs gyur pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-10: chags med de dag spyod yul sa 'di yin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-11: nyon mongs med sems bskyod med spyod ldan zhing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-12: gang rnams 'gyod pa rnams bsal la sems ldan te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-13: sangs rgyas gdams ngag nan tan byed ldan pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-14: dri med de dag spyod yul 'di yin no; ;gang rnams mi sgul sems ldan mi bskyod sems //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-15: chos kyi rang bzhin rtogs pa'i sems ldan zhing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-16: las kyi rgya mtshor mi 'gal sems ldan pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-17: mi bzad de dag rnam thar 'di yin no //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-18: gang rnams mi skyo'i sems dang mi ldog sems //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-19: brtson 'grus mthu dang rtsal du ldan pa rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-20: thams cad mkhyen tshogs brtson 'grus mtha' yas pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-21: brtul zhugs bzang ldan de dag yul 'di yin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-22: zhi ba'i sems ldan mnyam par bzhag pa gang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:50b-23: shin tu zhir gyur rim dang bral ba rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-1: mkhyen bsam gtan yan lag mchor spyod pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-2: rab tu zhi ba de dag tshul 'di yin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-3: gang rnams chags pa kun las sems grol zhing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-4: chos kyi rang bzhin khong du chud sems can //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-5: rgyal ba'i chos dbyings rtogs par khong chud pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-6: shes rab sgron ma de dag tshul 'di yin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-7: sems can rang bzhin rtogs sems ldan gyur cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-8: gang rnams srid pa'i mtsho la chags med sems //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-9: sems can sems la gzugs brnyan zla 'char ba //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-10: lam mkhan de dag rnam thar 'di yin no; ;dus gsum byung ba'i rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-11: smon lam gang chen mtsho rgyud skyes pa yi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-12: zhing rnams kun tu phyi ma'i mthar spyod pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-13: kun tu bzang po de dag tshul 'di yin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-14: gang rnams chos dbyings tshul rnams rgya mtsho yis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-15: 'gro ba rgya mtsho 'du dang 'jig pa yi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-16: bskal par bcas pa khong du chud pa rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-17: rtog med de dag rnam thar 'di yin no //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-18: zhing rnams kun gyi rdul phran thams cad la //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-19: sangs rgyas grangs med shing rgyal drung bzhugs shing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-20: byang chub 'tshang rgya 'gro 'dul mthong ba yi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-21: chags med dmigs can de dag tshul 'di yin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-22: khyod ni bskal pa rgya mtsho rgya chen du //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51a-23: dge ba'i bshes gnyen mang po bsnyen bkur te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-0: chos @51b 'dod chos tshol mi skyo 'dir phyin pas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-1: thos nas de ni yongs su gzung bar nus //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-2: khyod kyi bsam pa yongs su sbyang ba'i phyir //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-3: bde gshegs byin rlabs bsam gyis mi khyab pas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-4: rnam par snang mdzad tshad med yul 'di yang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-5: kho mo'i tshig las chags pa med par 'byung //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-7: sngon byung ba'i dus bskal pa 'jig rten gyi khams
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-8: kyi rdul shin tu phra ba snyed kyi pha rol
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-9: de'i yang pha snga zhig tu 'jig rten gyi khams
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-10: rgya mtsho gser rin po che'i ri spos rnam par
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-11: snang ba zhes bya ba byung ste /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-13: 'jig rten gyi khams rgya mtsho gser rin po che'i
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-14: ri spos rnam par snang ba der de bzhin gshegs
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-15: pa ye shes ri bo'i 'od chos kyi dbyings su
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-16: snang ba'i gzi brjid rgyal po zhes bya ba byung
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-17: ste / de bzhin gshegs pa ye shes kyi ri
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-18: bo'i 'od chos kyi dbyings su snang ba'i gzi brjid
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:51b-19: ste / rgyal po de / sngon byang chub sems

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:158b-25: bud med rin chen 'jig rten 'dir byung ste //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-1: rab brgyan pa'i sku gzugs mdzes mnga' ba //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-3: 'di ni ha cang mi ring mi thung ste //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-5: yan lag skyon bral 'di ni khyod la 'os //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-6: grangs dang yi ge shes bgyi tshul rnams dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-7: lag brda'i tshul dang gtsug lag tshul la mkhas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-8: 'jig rten kun na bzo rnams ji snyed pa //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-12: 'di ni mchog tu pha rol phyin par gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-13: lus rnams kun nas rin chen rnam dag pa'i //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-14: 'od mchog 'khor gyis shin tu mdzes pa ste //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-15: sngon gyi legs pas shin tu sdug par brgyan //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-16: 'di ni khyod kyi phyag rjed khyod la 'os //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-17: mi yi 'jig rten gnas rnams ji snyed pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-18: de dag gso ba'i tshul gyi cho ga 'tshal; ;de dag ma lus thams cad zhir bgyi na'ang //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-21: skye bo'i nges tshig ma lus bye brag dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-22: 'jig rten tha snyad brjod pa'i mtshams sbyar ba //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-23: sna tshogs kun la'ang 'di ni pha rol phyin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159a-24: dbyangs kyi yan lag mngon par sgrub pa'i tshul //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-0: de dag bye brag tshul la'ang @159b rab tu zhugs //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-1: 'jig rten glu gar rnam pa ji snyed pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-2: ma lus de rnams kun gyi tshul yang 'tshal //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-3: rol mo sil snyan dag gi thabs rnams dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-4: bzhad gad rol mo'i tshul la rnam par mkhas; ;chags dang ma chags mi rnams mngon 'tshal kyang //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-7: khyad par nang du de la ma lus 'tshal; ;bud med skye bo'i skyon du bgyi ba rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-8: grangs med de dag 'di la gcig ma mchis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-9: thil gyis blta dang zur gyis blta ba dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-10: yan lag bstabs dang yan lag rnams bstan dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-11: shes nyen kun la mkhas pa'i mthar phyin te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-12: khyod kyi dgongs pa yongs su rdzogs par bgyid //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-13: 'di ni phrag dog ser sna ma mchis te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-14: 'dod pa zhe dug mi ldang sdig mi bgyid //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-15: bzod cing drang la mnyen zhing des pa ste //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-16: mi khro mi brlang shin tu mkhas pa lags //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:159b-17: ldang ba'i ngang tshul yid du'ong ba'i ngag /

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:160a-10: 'di ni gang la'ang chags par 'gyur ma mchis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:160a-11: dge ba shes rnams la sri zhu 'di che ste //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:160a-23: pa'i ma sprul tshong ma'i gtso mo blta na sdug

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:160b-19: mtha' las rgal bar bde ba la ni /

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-6: de ltar bdog pa thams cad yongs su gtong ba
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-7: la nan tan nyams su len pa'i tshe phyi nang
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-8: gi dngos po gang ci yang rung ste /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-9: yongs su mi gtang ba de lta bu med pas de ltar ngas bu dang /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-11: chung ma yang sbyin par bya dgos //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-16: nying lag thams cad kyang yongs su gtang dgos na /

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-18: nga'i sbyin pa'i bgegs su 'gyur ro //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-19: bu yid du 'ong ba yongs su btang na /

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-22: nga la bdog pa thams cad yongs su btang bar byas na /

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-29: / de'i tshe'ang khyod yid mi dga' bar 'gyur ro //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161a-30: zhes nas rgyal bu gzi brjid bdag pos de'i tshe
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-0: bu mo @161b dga' ba'i 'od kyi dpal shin tu
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-1: sbyangs pa la tshigs su bcad de smras pa /

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-5: tshad med thams cad yongs su rdzogs bya dgos //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-6: bskal pa rgya mtsho mtha' dang dbus med par //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-7: mkha' ltar tshad med smon lam rnam sbyang zhing //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-9: bskal pa mtha' yas yongs su sbyang yang dgos //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-10: rgyal ba dus gsum 'byung ba thams cad kyi //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-16: 'jig rten kun gyi mi khom thams cad dang //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-22: chags med sa rnams kun kyang ngas sbyangs te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:161b-23: bskal ba rgya mtshor rgyal ba mchod par bya //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:162a-4: nga yi mgo 'dod 'ongs par ngas mthong ste //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:162a-5: byang chub sems dpa'i spyad pa spyod gyur na //

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:162a-15: khyod dga' thams cad de bzhin bya la rag /

K09D0044-6_H0094-6:337b-25: grul bum dag dang mi yi skad rnams dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:337b-26: 'gro ba kun gyi sgra rnams ji tsam par //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-2: des shing pha rol phyin la rab brtson te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-3: byang chub sems ni nam yang brjed ma gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-4: sdig pa gang rnams sgrib par 'gyur ba dag /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-5: de dag ma lus yongs su byang bar shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-6: las dang nyon mongs bdud kyi las rnams las //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-7: grol zhing 'jig rten 'gro ba rnams su yang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-8: ji ltar padmo rgyus mi chags pa bzhin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-9: nyi zla nam mkhar thogs pa med ltar spyad //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-10: zhing gi khyon dang phyogs rnams ji tsam par //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-11: ngan song sdug bsngal rab tu zhi bar byed; ;bde ba dag la 'gro ba kun 'god cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-12: 'gro ba thams cad la ni phan par spyad //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-13: byang chub spyod pa yongs su rdzogs byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-14: sems can dag gi spyod dang mthun par 'jug /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-15: bzang po spyod pa dag ni rab ston cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-16: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyod par gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-17: bdag gi spyod dang mtshungs par gang spyod pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-18: de dag dang ni rtag tu 'grogs par shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-19: lus dang ngag rnams dang ni sems kyis kyang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-20: spyod pa dag dang smon lam gcig tu spyad //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-21: bdag la phan par 'dod pa'i grogs po dag /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-22: bzang po spyod pa rab tu ston pa rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-23: de dag dang yang rtag tu phrad par shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338a-24: de dag bdag gis nam yang yid mi dbyung //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-0: sangs rgyas sras kyis bskor ba'i mgon po @338b rnams; ;mngon sum rtag tu bdag gis rgyal ba blta //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-1: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu mi skyo bar //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-2: de dag la yang mchod pa rgya cher bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-3: rgyal ba rnams kyi dam pa'i chos 'dzin cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-4: byang chub spyod pa kun tu snang bar byed //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-5: bzang po spyod pa rnam par spyod pa yang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-6: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu spyad par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-7: srid pa thams cad du yang 'khor ba na //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-8: bsod nams ye shes dag ni mi zad rnyed //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-9: thabs dang shes rab ting 'dzin rnam thar dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-10: yon tan kun gyi mi zad mdzod du gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-11: rdul gcig steng na rdul snyed zhing rnams te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-12: zhing der bsam gyis mi khyab sangs rgyas rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-13: sangs rgyas sras kyi dbus na bzhugs pa la //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-14: byang chub spyad pa spyod cing blta bar bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-15: de ltar ma lus thams cad phyogs su yang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-16: skra tsam khyon la dus gsum tshad snyed kyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-17: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho zhing rnams rgya mtsho dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-18: bskal pa rgya mtshor spyod cing rab tu 'jug /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-19: gsung gcig yan lag rgya mtsho'i sgra skad kyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-20: rgyal ba kun dbyangs yan lag rnam dag pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-21: 'gro ba kun gyi bsam pa ji bzhin dbyangs //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-22: sangs rgyas gsung la rtag tu 'jug par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-23: dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad dag /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-24: 'khor lo tshul rnams rab tu bskor ba yi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-25: de dag gi yang gsung dbyangs mi zad la //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:338b-26: blo yi stobs kyis bdag kyang rab tu 'jug /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-1: bskal pa thams cad 'jug par yang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-2: skad cig gcig gis bdag kyang 'jug par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-3: gang yang bskal pa dus gsum tshad de dag /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-4: skad cig cha shas kyis ni zhugs par spyad //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-5: dus gsum gshegs pa mi yi sengge dag /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-6: de dag skad cig gcig la bdag gis blta //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-7: rtag tu de dag gi ni spyod yul la //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-8: sgyu mar gyur pa'i rnam thar stobs kyis 'jug /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-9: gang yang dus gsum dag gi zhing bkod pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-10: de dag rdul gcig steng du mngon par sgrub //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-11: de ltar ma lus phyogs rnams thams cad du //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-12: rgyal ba rnams kyi zhing gi rgyan la 'jug /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-13: gang yang ma byon 'jig rten sgron ma rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-14: de dag rim par 'tshang rgya 'khor lo bskor //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-15: mya ngan 'das pa rab tu zhi mtha' ston //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-16: mgon po kun gyi drung du bdag mchi'o //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-17: kun tu myur ba'i rdzu 'phrul stobs rnams dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-18: kun nas sgo yi theg pa'i stobs dag dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-19: kun tu yon tan spyod pa'i stobs rnams dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-20: kun tu khyab pa byams pa dag gi stobs //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-21: kun tu dge ba'i bsod nams stobs rnams dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-22: chags pa med par gyur pa'i ye shes stobs //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-23: shes rab thabs dang ting 'dzin stobs dag gis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-24: byang chub stobs rnams yang dag sgrub par byed //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339a-25: las kyi stobs rnams yongs su dag byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-0: nyon mongs stobs @339b rnams kun tu 'joms par byed //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-1: bdud kyi stobs rnams stobs med rab byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-2: bzang po spyod pa'i stobs ni rdzogs par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-3: zhing rnams rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-4: sems can rgya mtsho dag ni rnam par sgrol //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-5: chos rnams rgya mtsho rab tu mthong byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-6: ye shes rgya mtsho rab tu rtogs par byed //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-7: spyod pa rgya mtsho rnam par dag byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-8: smon lam rgya mtsho rab tu rdzogs par byed //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-9: sangs rgyas rgya mtsho rab tu mchod byed cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-10: bskal pa rgya mtshor mi skyo spyad par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-11: gang yang dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba yi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-12: byang chub spyod pa'i smon lam bye brag rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-13: bzang po spyod pas byang chub sangs rgyas nas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-14: de kun bdag gis ma lus rdzogs par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-15: rgyal ba kun gyi sras kyi thu bo pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-16: gang gi ming ni kun tu bzang zhes bya; ;mkhas pa de dang mtshungs par spyad pa'i phyir //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-17: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-18: lus dang ngag dang yid kyang rnam dag cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-19: spyod pa rnam dag zhing rnams yongs dag dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-20: bsngo ba bzang po mkhas pa ci 'dra ba //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-21: de 'drar bdag kyang de dang mtshungs par shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-22: kun nas dge ba bzang po spyad pa'i phyir //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-23: 'jam dpal gyi ni smon lam spyad par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-24: ma 'ongs bskal pa kun tu mi skyo bar //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-25: de yi bya ba ma lus rdzogs par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-26: spyod pa dag ni tshad yod ma gyur cig /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:339b-27: yon tan rnams kyang tshad gzung med par shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-2: de dag 'phrul pa thams cad 'tshal bar bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-3: nam mkha'i mthar thug gyur pa ji tsam par //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-4: sems can ma lus mtha' yang de bzhin te; ;ji tsam las dang nyon mongs mthar gyur pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-5: bdag gi smon lam mtha' yang de tsam mo //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-6: gang yang phyogs bcu'i zhing rnams mtha' yas pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-7: rin chen brgyan te rgyal ba rnams la phul; ;lha dang mi yi bde ba mchog rnams kyang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-8: zhing gi rdul snyed bskal par phul ba bas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-9: gang gis bsngo ba'i rgyal po 'di thos nas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-10: byang chub mchog gi rjes su rab mos shing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-11: lan gcig tsam yang dad pa bskyed pa ni //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-12: bsod nams dam pa'i mchog tu 'di 'gyur ro //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-13: gang gis bzang spyod smon lam 'di btab pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-14: des ni ngan song thams cad spong bar 'gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-15: des ni grogs po ngan pa'ang spangs pa yin //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-16: snang ba mtha' yas de yang des myur mthong //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-17: de dag rnyed pa rab rnyed bde bar 'tsho //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-18: mi tsho 'dir yang de dag legs par 'ongs; ;kun tu bzang po de yang ci 'dra bar //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-19: de dag ring por mi thogs de bzhin 'gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-20: mtshams med lnga po dag gi sdig pa rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-21: gang gis mi shes dbang gis byas pa dag /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-22: de yis bzang po'i spyod pa 'di brjod na //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-23: myur du ma lus yongs su byang bar 'gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340a-24: ye shes dang ni gzugs dang mtshan rnams dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-0: rigs dang kha dog rnams dang ldan par @340b 'gyur; ;bdud dang mu stegs mang pos de mi thub //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-1: 'jig rten gsum po kun na'ang mchod par 'gyur //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-2: byang chub shing dbang drung du de myur 'gro /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-3: song nas sems can phan phyir de 'dug ste; ;byang chub sangs rgyas 'khor lo rab tu bskor //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-4: bdud rnams sde dang bcas pa thams cad btul //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-5: gang yang bzang po spyod pa'i smon lam 'di //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-6: 'chang ba dang ni ston tam klog na yang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-7: de yi rnam par smin pa sangs rgyas mkhyen //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-8: byang chub mchog la som nyi ma byed cig /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-9: 'jam dpal ji ltar mkhyen cing dpa' ba dang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-10: kun tu bzang po de yang de bzhin te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-11: de dag gi ni rjes su bdag slob cing //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-12: dge ba 'di dag thams cad rab tu bsngo //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-13: dus gsum gshegs pa'i rgyal ba thams cad kyis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-14: bsngo ba gang la mchog tu bsngags pa des //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-15: bdag gi dge ba'i rtsa ba 'di kun kyang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-16: bzang po spyod phyir rab tu bsngo bar bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-17: bdag ni 'chi ba'i dus byed gyur pa na //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-18: sgrib pa thams cad bdag ni phyir bsal te //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-19: mngon sum snang ba mtha' yas de mthong nas /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-20: bde ba can gyi zhing der rab tu 'gro /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-21: der song nas ni smon lam 'di dag kyang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-22: thams cad ma lus mngon du gyur par shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-23: de dag ma lus bdag gis yongs su bkang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-24: 'jig rten ji srid sems can phan par bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-25: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor bzang zhing dga' ba der //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-26: padmo dam pa shin tu mdzes las skyes //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:340b-27: snang ba mtha' yas rgyal bas mngon sum du //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-1: yang bdag gis der thob shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-2: der ni bdag gis lung bstan rab thob nas //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-3: sprul pa mang po bye ba phrag brgya yis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-4: blo yi stobs kyis phyogs bcu rnams su yang //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-5: sems can rnams la phan pa mang po bgyi //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-6: gang gis bzang po spyod pa ston pa yis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-7: dge ba cung zad bdag gis ci bsags pa //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-8: des ni 'gro ba'i smon lam dge ba rnams; ;skad cig gcig gis thams cad 'byor par shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-9: gang yang bzang po spyod pa bsngos pa yis //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-10: bsod nams mtha' yas dam pa thob pa des //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-11: 'gro ba sdug bsngal chu bor bying ba rnams //
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-12: 'od dpag med pa'i gnas rab 'gro bar shog /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-13: shin tu rgyas pa chen po'i mdo /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-14: sangs rgyas phal po che zhes bya ba las /
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-15: byang chub sems dpa'i sde snod kyi nang nas sdong
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-16: pos brgyan pa zhes bya ba chos kyi rnam grangs
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-17: chen po las nor bzang gis dge ba'i bshes gnyen
K09D0044-6_H0094-6:341a-18: bsnyen bkur ba'i spyod pa phyogs gcig pa ste /
